# Weather App

A simple web app that fetches and displays current weather data for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API.

## Features
- Enter a city name and see the current temperature and weather description
- Uses OpenWeatherMap's free API
- Clean, responsive UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Fetch API)
- OpenWeatherMap API

## Live Demo
[View Weather App](https://yadrielpereyra.github.io/weather-app/)

## How to Use
1. Enter a city name in the input field.
2. Click **"Get Weather"**.
3. The app will display the current temperature and weather description.

## Setup (Local)
1. Clone the repository.
2. Get a free API key from [OpenWeatherMap](https://openweathermap.org/api).
3. Replace `'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE'` in the `script.js` file with your API key.
4. Open `index.html` in your browser.

